io.github.u004.steamid.utils

Class USteamAccount

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.steamid.utils.USteamAccount

  • public final class USteamAccount
extends Object
    A Steam account types utility.

    USteamAccount is the utility class for all types of Steam accounts that contain account type IDs and chars associated with these IDs.

    Since:
    0.1.0
    See Also:
    Steam Account Types
